[[File:Shipyard_256.png|left|128px]]
Enables recruitment of naval units and, if upgraded, increases their recruitment speed. Placing a Barracks nearby further increases recruitment speed.

'''Requires:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 10
{{Main|Shipyard}}

==Camouflage Trap==

[[File:Wall_tower_nebel.png|left|128px]]
Camouflage Trap neutralize the troop strength of a limited number of enemy artillery units. Neutralized attackers will not deal damage to defenders, fortifications and buildings. A maximum of 50% of artillery units will be affected. Camouflage Traps can only be built on the outer ring of the City Wall, and don’t count towards a city’s building number limit.

'''Requires:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 10
{{Main|Camouflage Trap}}
